{"tid":1165082,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美股升都無用,港股一樣都係跌","createTime":"2019-05-21T14:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T14:28:33.000Z","uid":190320,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59662306d17db7bb48305ee9d285954c751d14d2","tid":1165082,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"- 人仔同港股存在 +ve Correlation, 人仔跌&gt;公司市值跌&gt;HSI 跌<br />\n- 今次貿易戰比上次中興既規模更大, 損害最大既係手機相關設備中資股。相反, 一啲係美國既上游供應商根本唔會有太大傷害,因為華為用少左,其他手機牌子公司變相要用返多啲,一樣要向上游供應商入貨。<br />\n<br />\n有錢真係投資多啲美股好過,港股根本就越來劣質中資股,越來越少投資價值<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美股就玩能源,港股就玩撚完<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09534138469ad23811f8d5a77380ff7f7ed60a8","tid":1165082,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好咁大聲"},{"pid":"1221e551c25acc64a46d435dde1c33fdea6a900f","tid":1165082,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"通常有價值既野 一多人知就少左價值 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}